data.description: Beautiful two bedroom, two full bath open concept ranch/bungalow in the heart of Orange City on a large corner lot in the Orange City Terrace Neighborhood. This lovely home has been beautifully maintained and has undergone a recent refresh. This home features an inside utility room, enclosed patio, one car garage, and 12 x 10 wood storage shed. If you have been looking for privacy and ample yard space look no further! This property is situated on a large corner .51 acre lot, which is fully fenced in and can only be accessed off of a secluded street. Recent upgrades include fresh paint, newer counter tops, vanities, vinyl plank flooring throughout, & new light fixtures. The large fenced yard is great for kids or pets. The property is FHA & USDA 100% loan eligible!
